The paper discusses tool-assisted refactoring transformations, which are typically associated with software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also proposes a notation for defining refactoring transformations in Erlang, which falls under programming languages (cs.PL). The paper emphasizes the importance of trustworthiness in refactoring, which relates to logic in computer science (cs.LO). The paper also discusses the verifiability and executability of the proposed notation, which falls under programming languages (cs.PL) and systems and control (cs.SY).
